reviews.text: Beside next to Khatib Camp Euphony Gardens Palm N C Neighbourhood Centre of Goodlink Park and Jalan Mata Ayer, this bus stop is walking distance to King of Strength Boxing Gym Shami Banana Leaf Delights and A&A Special Restaurant for Indian Muslim Food Hongkong Muslim Seafood Briyani and Prasta. Freshly prepared food with healthy ingredients tender loving skillful cooking and warm services. In addition to buses serving Woodlands Admiralty Sembawang Canberra Yishun Khatib there are buses 169 and 860 to Ang Mo Kio 171 to Marina Square 167 to Bukit Merah 980 to Geylang via Thomson and buses to Sembawang Shopping Centre and Sembawang MRT bus interchange Sun Plaza with plenty of dinning shopping banking supermarkets groceries sundries postage services community centre and amenities nearby. Walking distance to Yishun Secondary School Jiemin Primary School Chong Pang Green AAVC Animal & Avian Veterinary Clinic Odles Learning Centre Cherry Kidz Montessori Childcare Cherie Hearts Nurture Cottage Daycare Centre Ginza Cafe Indian Cuisine Paradise Biryani McDonald's Domino's Pizza Canadian Pizza Shi Shang Chuan Wei Hot Pot Hai Lu Feng Roasted Delights and the Daily Scoop Icecream. Friendly cosy comfy welcoming ambience for romantic intimates groups students expats locals visitors and families.
The bus stop has just been relocated a few meters behind and is also the side as the opposite bus stop for the upcoming NSC project
Should include more bus services here.
